    id: "puffin-4",
    label: "Pattern matching: constructors, guards, case",
    code: ";; pattern matching: constructor patterns over an ADT, guards,\n;; literals inside constructors, bare nullary constructors, and _\n;; (docs/TYPES.md) -- plus vectors and case\n(define-type Shape\n  (Point)\n  (Circle Int)\n  (Rect Int Int))\n(define (classify [s : Shape]) : Sym\n  (match s\n    [Point 'point]\n    [(Circle r) #:when (< r 0) 'invalid]\n    [(Circle 0) 'degenerate]\n    [(Circle _) 'circle]\n    [(Rect w h) #:when (eq? w h) 'square]\n    [_ 'rectangle]))\n(println (classify Point))\n(println (classify (Circle -5)))\n(println (classify (Circle 0)))\n(println (classify (Circle 12)))\n(println (classify (Rect 4 4)))\n(println (classify (Rect 4 2)))\n\n;; constructor patterns nest, like every other pattern\n(define-type (Tree a)\n  (Leaf)\n  (Node (Tree a) a (Tree a)))\n(define (shallow? t)\n  (match t\n    [Leaf #t]\n    [(Node Leaf _ Leaf) #t]\n    [_ #f]))\n(println (shallow? (Node Leaf 'x Leaf)))\n(println (shallow? (Node (Node Leaf 'x Leaf) 'y Leaf)))\n\n;; vector + list patterns still work on plain data\n(define (peek v)\n  (match v\n    [(vector a b) (list 'pair-vec a b)]\n    [(list) 'empty]\n    [(list x) (list 'singleton x)]\n    [_ 'other]))\n(println (peek (vector 1 2)))\n(println (peek '()))\n(println (peek (list 42)))\n(case (+ 1 2) [(1 2) (println 'low)] [(3 4) (println 'mid)] [else (println 'high)])\n",
